  <summary date="2017-02-21T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Burial Rights for America's Veterans' Efforts Act of 2017 or the BRAVE Act of 2017

This bill increases the amounts payable through the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) for: (1) burial and funeral expenses of certain veterans, and (2) such expenses in connection with a veteran's death due to a service-connected disability.

 The VA shall increase such amounts each fiscal year by the percentage increase in the Consumer Price Index.</summary>
